Feature: Forbidden flow
    Cannot perform some actions when PR / repo is in invalid state


    Scenario: Cannot merge enqueued PR until it is good
        Given PR '1' exists
        And   PR '1' was enqueued

        When Flow starts
        Then Branch 'target' does not match branch 'queue' yet
        And  PR '1' cannot be merged yet
        And  Push was called '0' times
        And  Branch 'target' does not match branch 'queue' still


    Scenario: Cannot merge enqueued PR marked bad
        Given PR '1' exists
        And   PR '1' was enqueued
        And   PR '1' was marked 'bad'

        When Flow starts
        Then Branch 'target' does not match branch 'queue' yet
        And  PR '1' cannot be merged yet
        And  Push was called '0' times
        And  Branch 'target' does not match branch 'queue' still


    Scenario: Cannot merge second PR with first in queue
        Given PR '1' exists
        And   PR '2' exists
        And   PR '1' was enqueued
        And   PR '2' was enqueued

        When Flow starts
        Then PR '2' cannot be merged yet
        And  Push was called '0' times
